{"tid":1678664,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"馬鈴薯大炮","createTime":"2019-10-27T18:20:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-27T21:35:52.000Z","uid":199606,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"6f2a42e4ae2596776faf124bbe39b078b349aee0","tid":1678664,"uid":199606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T18:20:49.000Z","msg":"上網睇啲人玩馬鈴薯大炮好似好好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有人自製大炮用PVC水管加瓦斯<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/sJxb7qcBuGA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FsJxb7qcBuGA&d=qY%2BFdmg29Nq5PZFqoXGv4eSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=930c3751\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/sJxb7qcBuGA</a><br />\n大炮仲可以分件組合<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/nZb_PKEubB8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FnZb_PKEubB8&d=qY%2BFdmg29Nq5PZFqoXGv4eSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=ab7af73a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/nZb_PKEubB8</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ykF3TUTI2hU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FykF3TUTI2hU&d=qY%2BFdmg29Nq5PZFqoXGv4eSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=fa1c543f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ykF3TUTI2hU</a><br />\n好似好危險 仲要幾枝都唔同整法<br />\n點知香港玩樣野犯唔犯法<br />\n同膛線點樣唔會爆炸<br />\n邊到可以買到黎玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申好危險純粹講下冇諗住玩 台灣玩好似冇犯法"},{"pid":"bed6b4c0f589a9ed303ce959ce8ea63eb0d0af36","tid":1678664,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T18:22:22.000Z","msg":"屌你老味識唔識中文"},{"pid":"07502857a1444c9f2b795295de125cbaaab878bb","tid":1678664,"uid":199606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bed6b4c0f589a9ed303ce959ce8ea63eb0d0af36","tid":1678664,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T18:22:22.000Z","msg":"屌你老味識唔識中文"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T18:23:42.000Z","msg":"係 請問邊隻字打錯"},{"pid":"d9dad6c97f3f37c95752c5d311d7f48473292c9a","tid":1678664,"uid":149878,"like":6,"dislik